author: COMSOL
description: This verification example is a uniaxial compression on a prestressed block. Due to simple prestresses and the uniaxial compression, it is possible to determine the yield stress of the material analytically. The block is modeled as an elastic-perfectly plastic material with Mohr–Coulomb yield criterion.
